description: ZetaDisplay AB engages in the provision of digital signage. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane and currently employs 200 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2011-04-04. The company operates through four geographical segments, namely Sweden, Norway, Denmark and Finland. The firm offers a media platform for Digital Signage, covering software, services and digital systems. Its solutions include analysis, consulting and project management. The Company’s customers are active in the retail and services industries in the Nordic market, and include Team Sportia, Audi and ICA. The firm has several subsidiaries, such as Flygstaben Fastighets AB, ZetaDisplay Sverige AB, ZetaDisplay Norge AS, ZetaDisplay Finland Oy, Marketmedia Oy, ZetaDisplay Danmark A/S and Seasam Oy.
naics: Advertising, Public Relations, and Related Services
